{
  "texts": [
    "After calculating the pairwise distance matrix between all proteins in the set of backbones, we apply hierarchical clustering with average linkage.",
    "This clustering is the same as performed by ref.",
    "15, which allows us to directly compare clustering results and plots.",
    "We apply this clustering procedure to protein sets generated by FoldingDiff, as well as a set of naturally occurring proteins to establish a reference.",
    "3D visualizations of protein structures are done via PyMOL 67."
  ]
}